long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Convert word (docx-doc) documents to pdf format.

How it works?
Click extension icon, it will then open our online converter website where you can convert word files to pdf.

When our webpage is open:
Select files from your computer or upload from dropbox, google drive or onedrive.
When files are uploaded, then you can convert them to pdf format.
